Explorer
As an Explorer, you now have your own Trading Tribe Account that you can access below and also on the Menu (upper left) under "My Account." On your My Account page, you may edit your profile, comprehension test, Issue and Service Project. You may also apply to join a Tribe, run a Tribe as its Chief or serve as a Mentor to help new Chiefs learn the ropes.
To do:
Join or Start a Tribe

Applicant
As an Applicant, you have your own Trading Tribe Account that you can access on the Resources Menu (upper left) under "My Account." You may also apply to join a Tribe, run a Tribe as its Chief or serve as a Mentor to help new Chiefs learn the ropes.
